POST {{baseUrl}}/user/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "username": "",
  "phone": "13800138000"
}

### ============================================
### 测试6: 参数校验 - 手机号为空
### 预期结果: 返回 "手机号不能为空"
